	<article class="post-157576 post type-post status-publish hentry category-fixes tag-boston-mass tag-domestic-service tag-labor-and-jobs tag-poo-ai-jen tag-womens-rights per-poo-ai-jen des-domestic-service des-labor-and-jobs des-womens-rights geo-boston-mass news_keywords-ai-jen-poo news_keywords-boston news_keywords-domestic-worker news_keywords-jobs-2 news_keywords-womens-rightsfeminism" id="post-157576">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="//opinionator.blogs.nytimes.com/category/fixes/?module=BlogCategory&version=Blog Post&action=Click&contentCollection=Opinion&pgtype=Blogs&region=Header">Fixes</a></span>
